# GloveCubs Commerce Truth

- Persisted database values are canonical over UI-calculated values.
- All money logic must use stored minor-unit values where available.
- Order totals must reconcile from canonical line, shipping, discount, tax, and total fields.
- Do not add fake, estimated, or fallback pricing in production paths unless explicitly labeled and approved.
- Customer-visible prices must trace to a trusted source.
- When pricing truth is unclear, stop and surface the ambiguity.